CatDescriptText: Headline for related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Out-of-Towners Enjoy Frogs' Swank Formal in Pittsburgh Room of Penn-Sheraton Hotel"
TitMainTitle: Men and women seated at "Robert Ratcliffe" table, possibly including Morris Fountain and Miriam Sharpe Fountain in background, Hubert Smith wearing eyeglasses, and Mrs. Smith on right, in ballroom of Penn Sheraton Hotel, for FROGS formal
